'Cause their own blood
can't sustain haemoglobin.

863
01:12:51,973 --> 01:12:53,391
Right. So it's
a genetic defect,

864
01:12:53,892 --> 01:12:54,601
just like
haemolytic anaemia.

865
01:12:55,059 --> 01:12:57,146
That means that
we have to treat it

866
