rewrite the victim's DNA
with a retrovirus.

868
01:13:01,233 --> 01:13:02,402
They've been using it
on sickle cell anaemia.

869
01:13:03,945 --> 01:13:05,031
Are you sure
that's safe?

870
01:13:05,490 --> 01:13:06,532
